data.text:
High School

Rated as the No. 28 linebacker in the country according to Rivals.com…Finished his senior season with 24 tackles, four tackles-for-loss, one forced fumble and a field goal block in eight appearances… Jones helped lead the St. Frances defense which averaged less than 15 points allowed-per-game during his senior season… During his junior season Jones led St. Frances to a 9-1 record, ranking at the top team in the state of Maryland and the No. 8 team nationally according to MaxPreps…During his sophomore season St. Frances finished the season 8-1, ranking at the top team in the state of Maryland and the No. 4 team nationally according to MaxPreps.

Personal

Son of Rhonda Jones… Born on January 27, 2005.
